SELECT * FROM tpch1g.orders ;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber,     l_quantity * 2 AS double_quantity,     l_extendedprice + 100 AS increased_price,     CONCAT(l_returnflag, l_linestatus) AS combined_status FROM tpch1g.lineitem ;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber,   SIN(l_quantity) AS sin_quantity,   COS(l_extendedprice) AS cos_price,   CONCAT(l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipinstruct) AS combined_status FROM tpch1g.lineitem ;
SELECT l_returnflag, sum(l_extendedprice * l_discount) as total_discounted_revenue FROM tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY l_returnflag;
SELECT SUM(EXP(l_quantity) + LOG(l_extendedprice) + SIN(l_discount) + COS(l_tax)) as complex_calculation FROM tpch1g.lineitem;
SELECT SUM(EXP(l_quantity) + LOG(l_extendedprice) + SIN(l_discount) + COS(l_tax)) as complex_calculation, COUNT(*) as total_count FROM tpch1g.lineitem;
SELECT SUM(EXP(l_quantity) + LOG(l_extendedprice) + SIN(l_discount) + COS(l_tax)) as complex_calculation, COUNT(*) as total_count, SUM(LENGTH(l_comment)) as total_comment_length FROM tpch1g.lineitem;

SELECT * FROM tpch1g.orders ;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_suppkey, l_linenumber, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipinstruct, l_shipmode, l_comment, SIN(l_quantity), COS(l_extendedprice), EXP(l_discount) FROM tpch1g.lineitem ;
SELECT o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderstatus, o_totalprice, o_orderdate, o_orderpriority, o_clerk, o_shippriority, o_comment, SIN(o_totalprice), COS(o_orderkey), EXP(o_custkey) FROM tpch1g.orders ;

SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderdate, o_totalprice, c_name, l_quantity, l_extendedprice FROM tpch1g.orders JOIN tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey JOIN tpch1g.lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey ORDER BY o_orderdate, o_orderkey;
SELECT * FROM tpch1g.lineitem JOIN tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey ORDER BY l_shipdate;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_extendedprice, o_orderdate, c_name, SIN(l_quantity), CONCAT(c_name, o_orderstatus) FROM tpch1g.lineitem JOIN tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey ORDER BY o_orderdate;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_extendedprice, o_orderdate, c_name, SIN(l_quantity), CONCAT(c_name, o_orderstatus) FROM tpch1g.lineitem JOIN tpch1g.orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey JOIN tpch1g.customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey ORDER BY o_orderdate, l_orderkey;
SELECT l_shipmode,         COUNT(*) AS count_orders,         SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extended_price  FROM tpch1g.lineitem  GROUP BY l_shipmode  ORDER BY total_extended_price DESC;

SELECT l_shipmode,     COUNT(*) AS count_orders,     SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extended_price,     SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 + l_discount)) AS adjusted_price,     AVG(LENGTH(l_comment)) AS avg_comment_length FROM tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY total_extended_price DESC;

SELECT l_shipmode,     COUNT(*) AS count_orders,     SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extended_price,     SUM(EXP(l_discount)) AS exp_discount_sum,     AVG(LENGTH(l_comment)) AS avg_comment_length FROM tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY total_extended_price DESC;

SELECT l_shipmode,     COUNT(*) AS count_orders,     SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extended_price,     SUM(EXP(l_discount)) AS exp_discount_sum,     AVG(LENGTH(l_comment)) AS avg_comment_length,     SUM(LOG(l_quantity + 1)) AS log_quantity_sum FROM tpch1g.lineitem GROUP BY l_shipmode ORDER BY total_extended_price DESC;
